-- MOVES-Eastspring Investments appoints head of marketing
-- 
-- Wed Sep 17, 2014 05:23AM EDT
-- None



Sept 17 (Reuters) - Eastspring Investments, the asset management arm of Prudential Corporation Asia, appointed Christian Fleischer as head of marketing and Tio Yang Phen as director of investment marketing.

Fleischer, who most recently worked at Blackrock Inc <BLK.N> in Europe, will focus on brand and marketing strategy and all communications initiatives and oversee the investment marketing group. Fleischer, based in Singapore, will report to Michele Bang, deputy chief executive.